\id 2JN - Border Kuna NT -Panama 2009 (DBL -2013)
\h 2 Juan
\toc1 Juan Ilabogus Karta Nermajad
\toc2 2 Juan
\toc3 2 Jn
\mt1 Juan Ilabogus Karta Nermajad
\mt2 2 Juan
\ip Imi Pab-Purpa-Nuedbal Juan iti-karta nermas kwenadganga choggal kwenadgan nuekwa tulemal-oturdadanimalad-takenabmal emalde chunchunnad Pabbal-naigusmalad o chul-dewa. Imi tulemal-oturdadanimalad chunchunnad-Pabbal-naichulil, kwenadgan melle tar-abingemalo. Pitomalgu.
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 Mu, imi Pab pe-chus. Tenal antin kwenadgan-iktuedga mai. Imi antin pega tegin pe-nuskanga karta wis palmijii.
\p Mu, imi antin Pab-igal-chunchunnadbal pemal-pilal, tenal antin, an anpi pe-kwen-pilalzhul, tenal tule-igal-chunchunnad-wismalad-pel-kwapa ampa pemal-pilalmalmo.
\v 2 Tenal igal-chunchunnad-anmalgin-maidbal, tegin we igal anmalbak ilagwen-nadgu kudiguoedbal, al an pemal-pilalmal.
\p 
\v 3 Imi Pab-Tummad-anmal-pab tegin e-Machi-Jesucristo pemalbak chunchunnad mailen, nabirin, tegin pemalga pilaledgin immal-nuegan imakelen, nabirbalin, tegin Pab wilejakwa pe-takelen, nabirbalin, tegin ulubgin akalzhul-itogal pemal-imakelen, nabirbalin.
\s1 Juan tule-pilalgued-igalgin chunmajad
\p 
\v 4 Mu, an itosdo, pe-nuskan-wal-walgwen igal-chunchunnadgin inniki nanedimal, Pab anmalga chogzhadyob. Al antin pe-nuskangin an naga ulubgin pela-pela weligwal itononi.
\p 
\v 5 Mu, an peje wiledo, pemal aga emal-emal pilalgumalgal. Tenal tule-pilalgued-igaldin, igal-pinzhul, tenal we igal kepe-sagla-akar anmalga choglesmaid.
\p 
\v 6 Imi tule-pilalgued-igal weobdo: imi anmal Pab-Jesús-chogzhad-pallí naneed-wilubmal. Tenal pe kepe-sagla-akar Pab-Jesús-chogzhad-itojad-yopí, pe pilalguedgin naneenabmal.
\s1 Tule-Cristo-igal-mamikid-opulomalad Pab-kwen-wichulmal
\p 
\v 7 Imi tule-yardamalad-ichejul iti-napkin aknismal. Tenal we tulemal chogmal, Jesucristo sanal kwen nonijul, pinche purpal noni. Tenal tulemal-teob-chogdimalad tule-yardamalad tegin Pabbak-aichulmalad.
\p 
\v 8 Tenal pe wijirmal, pe nue aga takermal, tule-iskana pe-yardadamal pe-Pabga-arpanaid melle pemalga ib-pinchegadga kunonigal tenal pe-Pabga-arpajadbal pel-kwapa pega uklegal.
\p 
\v 9 Imi meke-ibi-tule Cristo-igal-mamikid-yopí kwen chunmajulil, tenal Cristo-igal-mamikid opulojal, we tule Pab-kwen-nikchul. Tenal meke-ibi-tule Cristo-igal-mamikid-yopí chunmadiil, aga ulubgin Pab-Tummad-nika, tegin Pab-Machi-nikabal.
\p 
\v 10 Imi meke-ibi-tule pe-negzhe nonikil, tenal Cristo-igal-mamikid-pallí inniki kwen chunmajulil, pe neggin melle we tule-odogo, tegin pe melle masgin we tule-okunno, tegin pe melle we tule-abingebalo.
\p 
\v 11 Tenal meke-ibi-tule, tule-noal-chunmadiid-abingeel, tule-noal-chunmaked-e-pakadga kunonimo.
\p 
\v 12 Tenal antin ichejul immal nika pemalga chunmagal. Tenal an kartagin pemalga nuekwá immal kwen chogbijul. Tenal an chogdé, an pemalzhe natapo. Tenal an pemalzhe nadel, anmal aga assapin chunmamalo anmal pela-pela weligwal-itogal.
\p 
\v 13 Imi Pab pe-urpa-chus. Tenal pe-urpa tegin e-nuskandin ampa pemalga kaka wis palmijimo. Pitomalgu.
